                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0798</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9932 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">灵山文化旅游集团的战略抉择：拈花湾该往何处去？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Where should Nianhua Bay go？The strategic choice of Lingshan Cultural Tourism Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱晋伟，沈伟晔</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无锡灵山文化旅游集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化旅游；战略决策；发展战略；特色小镇；2018百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">culture tourism; strategic choice; development strategy; characteristic town</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无锡灵山•拈花湾是灵山文化旅游集团旗下的一个以禅意文化为主题的旅游度假体验区。拈花湾以精品意识为引领，开展了独特的经营管理活动。为了打造东方禅意生活乐土、世界心灵度假花园，建设了别具一格的禅意文化旅游产品，开园以来发展顺利，吸引了国内外大批游客并获得了广泛好评，成为继灵山大佛、九龙灌浴、灵山梵宫之后，灵山文化旅游集团又一具有国际影响力的市场领导品牌。但是，面对国内兴起的旅游特色小镇热潮、市场竞争的加剧，拈花湾建设投入成本高、回报时间长、消费者新奇感边际效用递减等潜在问题显现，今后应该实施怎样的战略，集团总经理沈君毅面临新的抉择。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Nianhua Bay in Wuxi city, operated by Lingshan Culture Tourism company, is a tourist vacation area themed with Zen Buddhist mood. Guided by a sense of boutique, Nianhua bay has carried out a series of unique activities. To create the oriental Zen paradise and the world-class soul holiday garden, a unique cultural tourist attraction has been produced. Nianhua Bay developed smoothly since the opening, attracted a large number of tourists at home and abroad and obtained good reputation. It becomes another leadership brand, the same as Lingshan Buddha, Kowloon bathing and Lingshan Vatican. However, with the booming of tourism characteristic town in China and the more fierce market competition, the potential problems such as high cost of investment, long return time and diminishing marginal utility of consumers&#39; novelty are emerging. What strategy should be implemented in the future, the general manager Shen Junyi faces a new choice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略管理 内外部环境分析</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
